k:text-red-100 mb-3\">🔥 问题:压倒性的氨气味</h3>\n                  <div class=\"text-red-800 dark:text-red-200 space-y-2\">\n                    <div><strong>原因:</strong> 除臭剂不足或盆清洁过期</div>\n                    <div><strong>解决方案:</strong> 加倍除臭剂用量,增加清洁频率至每天两次</div>\n                    <div><strong>预防:</strong> 永远不要跳过晚间维护程序</div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"border-l-4 border-yellow-500 dark:border-yellow-700 bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/20 p-6\">\n                  <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-yellow-900 dark:text-yellow-100 mb-3\">⚠️ 问题:一个盆比其他盆气味更重</h3>\n                  <div class=\"text-yellow-800 dark:text-yellow-200 space-y-2\">\n                    <div><strong>原因:</strong> 领地偏好或一只猫的医疗问题</div>\n                    <div><strong>解决方案:</strong> 问题盆使用三倍除臭剂,检查潜在健康问题</div>\n                    <div><strong>预防:</strong> 监测每只猫的如厕习惯</div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"border-l-4 border-blue-500 dark:border-blue-700 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 p-6\">\n                  <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-100 mb-3\">💙 问题:猫避开某些盆</h3>\n                  <div class=\"text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-200 space-y-2\">\n                    <div><strong>原因:</strong> 过度除臭或使用香味产品</div>\n                    <div><strong>解决方案:</strong> 减少除臭剂一半,确保无香配方</div>\n                    <div><strong>预防:</strong> 始终使用无香天然除臭剂,如活性炭</div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div class=\"bg-[#FF3131]/10 dark:bg-[#FF3131]/5 border border-[#FF3131]/20 dark:border-[#FF6B6B]/30 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8\">\n                <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[#FF3131] dark:text-[#FF6B6B] mb-4\">🏆 为什么Purrify是多猫家庭的第一选择</h3>\n                <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\">\n                  <div class=\"space-y-3\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start space-x-2\">\n        